title: Episode 110 | Cyhi the Prynce on Kanye, Virgil, & Writing ‘Sicko Mode’
description: This week the guys are joined by Hip-Hop legend, Cyhi the Prynce to discuss paying for samples, the importance of a marketing budget, the "college" era of hip-hop, top 5 artists of the moment, the negative connotation on ghost writing, drug rap vs drill rap, Kanye's GAP & Adidas beef, Cyhi's favorite G.O.O.D. Music artists, and much more.
author: newrorymal@gmail.com (More Sauce)
